emirates gained independence in one nine seven one oil wealth continued to flow 
to the area and traditional mud brick huts were rapidly replaced with banks 
boutiques and modern highrises current ruler his highness sheikh khalifa bin 
zayed al nahayan is the hereditary emir and ruler of abu dhabi as well as the 
current president of the united arab emirates uae postal history shaikh zaid 
